could go into their own neighborhood city hall and 
they wouldn't feel so intimidated about

26:18.029 --> 26:31.308
appearing in a municipal edifice. They would 
happen to be a trader in their neighborhood park,

26:31.328 --> 26:42.664
whereas they might feel somewhat more 
apprehensive about coming to city hall and

26:31.328 --> 26:42.664
attending a city council meeting. Well, of 
