26:45.518 --> 26:49.522
throughout the country, I think, was show the 
people the way to city hall. It did so here. And we

26:51.324 --> 27:00.073
have numerous citizens appearing before the city 
council as well as getting calls all day about

26:51.324 --> 27:00.073
complaints. We don't have as active an inspection 
and keeping our own house because of just the sheer

27:12.603 --> 27:16.789
570 square miles of the city because people ride 
around trying to find things wrong. We barely can

27:17.450 --> 27:18.412
do that. The city has gotten much more responsive, 
I think, with the new council since we switched

27:18.452 --> 27:34.215
from an at-large to a district council at 
answering citizen complaints. But it's

27:34.355 --> 27:38.982
basically up to the citizen to say, hey, my 
street's messed up or hey, my water line's broken

27:39.518 --> 27:48.689
because we just don't have the resources to do 
